item.title: Fall Books
item.description: Books for the fall Here are a list of books I am currently intersted in this fall, this are to help me understand concept I sometimes struggle to understand. Being passionate about learning, I like to keep myself updated with the latest trends in computer science. This could be improvement in a certain aspect of a specific programming language or something covering the current state of the art research.
